    <summary><span data-ttu-id="40ff0-101">使用組態檔中 ASP.NET <see langword="&lt;machineKey&gt;" /> 元素指定的簽署和加密金鑰，處理工作階段權杖。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-101">Processes session tokens by using signing and encryption keys specified in the ASP.NET <see langword="&lt;machineKey&gt;" /> element in a configuration file.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-102">根據預設，<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler>類別會使用<xref:System.IdentityModel.ProtectedDataCookieTransform>類別，可使用 「 資料保護 API (DPAPI)，來保護工作階段權杖。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-102">By default, the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler> class uses the <xref:System.IdentityModel.ProtectedDataCookieTransform> class, which uses the Data Protection API (DPAPI), to protect the session token.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-103">DPAPI 透過使用者或電腦認證來提供保護，並將金鑰資料儲存在使用者設定檔中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-103">The DPAPI provides protection by using the user or machine credentials and stores the key data in the user profile.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-104">這表示工作階段權杖簽署和加密一部電腦上無法驗證，或在不同的電腦上解密。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-104">This means that a session token signed and encrypted on one computer cannot be validated or decrypted on a different computer.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-105">相反地，<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Tokens.MachineKeySessionSecurityTokenHandler>類別會使用<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.MachineKeyTransform>類別，藉由使用指定的加密編譯內容保護工作階段 cookie 資料`<machineKey>`組態檔中的項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-105">By contrast, the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Tokens.MachineKeySessionSecurityTokenHandler> class uses the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.MachineKeyTransform> class, which protects the session cookie data by using the cryptographic material specified in the `<machineKey>` element in the configuration file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-106">這表示相同的金鑰 （和工作階段權杖），可以使用多部電腦上。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-106">This means that the same keys (and session tokens) can be used across multiple computers.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-107">Web 伺服陣列中部署應用程式時，這是特別重要。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-107">This is particularly important when an application is deployed in a web farm.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-108">如需如何使用 Windows Identity Foundation 來保護部署在 web 伺服陣列中的應用程式的詳細資訊，請參閱[WIF 和 Web 伺服陣列](~/docs/framework/security/wif-and-web-farms.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-108">For more information about how to use Windows Identity Foundation to protect applications that are deployed in a web farm, see [WIF and Web Farms](~/docs/framework/security/wif-and-web-farms.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-109">設定應用程式以使用 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Tokens.MachineKeySessionSecurityTokenHandler>，做法為將它加入到權杖處理常式集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-109">Configure the application to use the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Tokens.MachineKeySessionSecurityTokenHandler> by adding it to the token handler collection.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-110">如果已有這類處理常式，您必須先從權杖處理常式集合中移除 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler> (或任何衍生自 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler> 類別的處理常式)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-110">You must first remove the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler> (or any handler derived from the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler> class) from the token handler collection if such a handler is present.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-111">這是因為<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Tokens.MachineKeySessionSecurityTokenHandler>衍生自<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler>權杖處理常式集合不能包含任何指定類型的多個處理常式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-111">This is because <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Tokens.MachineKeySessionSecurityTokenHandler> derives from <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler> and a token handler collection cannot contain multiple handlers of any given type.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-112">下列 XML 示範如何使用 ASP.NET`<machineKey>`中明確指定簽署和加密金鑰的組態項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-112">The following XML shows how to use the ASP.NET `<machineKey>` element in configuration to explicitly specify signing and encryption keys.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-113">`<machineKey>`下，項目會指定`<system.web>`組態檔中的項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-113">The `<machineKey>` element is specified under the `<system.web>` element in a configuration file.</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<machineKey compatibilityMode="Framework45" decryptionKey="CC510D … 8925E6" validationKey="BEAC8 … 6A4B1DE" />  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-114">下列 XML 示範如何將 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Tokens.MachineKeySessionSecurityTokenHandler> 新增到權杖處理常式集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-114">The following XML shows how to add the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Tokens.MachineKeySessionSecurityTokenHandler> to a token handler collection.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-115">預設值<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler>第一次從集合中移除。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-115">The default <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler> is first removed from the collection.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="40ff0-116">權杖處理常式設定下[ &lt;securityTokenHandlers&gt; ](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/windows-identity-foundation/securitytokenhandlers.md)項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="40ff0-116">Token handlers are configured under the [&lt;securityTokenHandlers&gt;](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/windows-identity-foundation/securitytokenhandlers.md) element.</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<securityTokenHandlers>  
  <remove type="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenHandler, System.IdentityModel, Version=4.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089" />  
  <add type="System.IdentityModel.Services.Tokens.MachineKeySessionSecurityTokenHandler, System.IdentityModel.Services, Version=4.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089" />  
</securityTokenHandlers>  
```  
  
 ]]></format>
